  subgraph SEQ_PHASE["Sequential Phase  [Agents 1вЂ“3]"]
    direction LR
    INGEST["Ingestion Agent\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nAccepts raw claim\nPublishes observations\nPython / LangChain"]
